6.5
<normalizedToken originalValue="–8.3–">-8.3-</normalizedToken>
10 
<normalizedToken originalValue="µm">µm</normalizedToken>
, either longer or shorter than the lateral cladi, 36
<normalizedToken originalValue="–61.6–">-61.6-</normalizedToken>
87 
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
4.5
<normalizedToken originalValue="–7.6–">-7.6-</normalizedToken>
10 
<normalizedToken originalValue="µm">µm</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
